    "role": "N/A",
    "person": "N/A",
    "content": "* Comms: What do we want for elections\n* Aiden: Starts monday, need story for debate and post for results. Will do a promo request for results / complete the whole team.\n* Magno: Is debate for everyone?\n* Aiden: Everyone running will debate (question period).\n* Cyrus: When is it?\n* Aiden: Saturday 4th",
